703
00:23:46,240 --> 00:23:46,580
 Ok.

704
00:23:46,580 --> 00:23:49,040
 Dakle, ja sam gospodin,

705
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:50,740
 Bog tvoga pravca Abrahama

706
00:23:50,740 --> 00:23:51,660
 i Bog Izakom.

707
00:23:51,660 --> 00:23:53,120
 Zemlju na kojoj ležiš

708
00:23:53,120 --> 00:23:54,860
